  "description": "THE CHANGE OF USE FROM A C4 HMO TO A  LARGE HMO (SUI GENERIS)  COMPRISING 3 x BEDSITS WITH OWN MICROWAVE AND SINK AND 3 x EN SUITE BEDROOMS SHARING KITCHEN/DINING ROOM ON GROUND FLOOR",
