  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed kitchen would be at ground floor level, two floor levels away from bedroom 5 and 6, this would result in an unsatisfactory standard of living to the detriment of the amenities of future occupiers and contrary to the HMO Licencing Requirements and policy D6 of the London Plan 2021.",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposals, by reason of the provision communal living/dining/kitchen space in the form of a single space, coupled with the likely occupancy levels of the HMO, and potential increased occupancy in the event of guests visiting the property, would result in a cramped and unsatisfactory environment for future occupiers contrary to London Plan (2021) Policy H9, Merton Core Planning Strategy policy CS14, Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014) DMH5 and London Borough of Merton Houses in Multiple Occupation (HMO) Requirements (Revised July 2021)  ",
    "Reason : 3 - The application has failed to demonstrate that the proposal is capable of providing cycle storage facilities, contrary to the London Plan (2021) Policy T5, Merton's Core Strategy (2011) Policy CS 18 and Merton's Sites and Policies Plan (2014) Policy DM T1.",
    "Reason : 4 - The application has failed to demonstrate that the proposal is capable of providing sufficient refuse and recycling facilities, contrary to the London Plan (2021) Policy SI 7 and Merton's Core Strategy Policy CS 17."
  ],
